{"tid":149161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【烈火雄心】私家車失控翻側消防局門外　多名消防員跑出救人","createTime":"2017-03-09T05:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T07:03:37.000Z","uid":73262,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ef7765989da787786fff447abb46f23b12e795","tid":149161,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:46:27.000Z","msg":"早上11時許，一輛白色私家車駛至常安街80號柴灣消防局外失控自炒，車身打橫掃向右翻側，撞至右邊路欄及路牌，一名途人閃避時跌在地上，在消防局內當值消防員聞訊，即跑出協助搶救私家車司機，被救出時半昏迷，消防為受傷途人及司機初步治理後，等候救護員將傷者送院。<br />\n<br />\n 救護員正為受傷途人包紮(馬路的事討論區fb圖片)<br />\n<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1692621/%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E7%BF%BB%E5%81%B4%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%B1%80%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E3%80%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1%E8%B7%91%E5%87%BA%E6%95%91%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1692621%2F%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E5%2581%25B4%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%2596%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c215da2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1692621/%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E7%BF%BB%E5%81%B4%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%B1%80%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E3%80%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1%E8%B7%91%E5%87%BA%E6%95%91%E4%BA%BA</a>"},{"pid":"a3223b0bf6444e4f96d7c2ffe7601491d51491b9","tid":149161,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"諗起急症室門外死都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n途人入去叫當值（唔知係咪護士）仲要叫佢叫十字車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91978e830d8a96e7dd4432c3c1b00bd2be5eca1c","tid":149161,"uid":75712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"